data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the heart of Dover, Florida! With 3570 square feet of living space and an array of impressive features, this property offers the perfect blend of luxury and comfort for your family's needs. As you arrive, you'll notice the expansive driveway and three-car garage with space for 6-7 cars which sets this property apart from the rest. The brand new Solar Panels are included in the price of this home.    The chef's dream kitchen boasts a grand marble backsplash over the oven, complemented by a convenient pot filler and a commercial-style vent hood. Enjoy the fully renovated kitchen featuring soft-close drawers and cabinets, with upper cabinets reaching the ceiling for both a high-end look and optimal storage capacity. The lower cabinets are designed as deep drawers for easy access, and the very high-end granite counters are backlit. The addition of a coffee bar and a wine/bar area with a built-in wine cooler adds a touch of elegance to your culinary experiences. The kitchen is complete with brand new Samsung kitchen appliances, including a new bespoke refrigerator. With the brand new washer and dryer that are also included in the price of this home.     The downstairs guest room has been thoughtfully designed as an in-law suite, offering added versatility to the home's layout. With multiple living areas, everyone can find their own space when needed. This remarkable home boasts a rare feature that movie enthusiasts and entertainment aficionados will instantly fall in love with - a private movie theater right within the comfort of your own space! Right outside the theater is a spacious and inviting loft area that adds a whole new dimension to your living space.     This home has been thoughtfully updated with modern amenities, including AC & air handlers replaced in 2019 and solar panels installed in December of 2021, ensuring energy efficiency. The tile flooring throughout the entire first floor is completely brand new. The roof was replaced in 2019, adding to the home's overall appeal and longevity. The primary suite master bathroom has also recently been updated.     Every detail has been carefully considered, with premium light fixtures, blinds, ceiling fans, & LED bulbs installed throughout the home.     Step into pure luxury and sophistication in this exquisite primary bedroom suite, thoughtfully designed to offer the utmost comfort and convenience. A true oasis awaits you, featuring not just one, but two spacious master closets.    Your escape from the world begins in the lavish primary bathroom, boasting an inviting garden tub where you can unwind and soak away the stresses of the day. Adjacent to the tub, a separate shower provides a spa-like experience, complete with modern fixtures and ample space for relaxation.    The patio extends the entire length of the home, providing an ideal space for outdoor living and entertainment. The generous yard offers plenty of room for your dream pool.    Location-wise, this home benefits from being in the sought-after Valrico Elementary school district. Enjoy the convenience of having three Publix locations within a 3-mile radius and Walmart, Home Depot, and Lowes less than 3 miles away.
